---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Pilot Program 2026"
  description="We're looking for 3 hotel kitchens to prove it with us in 2026. Pilot conditions, direct line to the founder, priority on everything."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="pt-28 pb-16 px-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-50/50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-brand-100 text-brand-700 text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-6">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-500 animate-pulse"></span>
        Pilot Program 2026
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
        We're Looking for 3 Hotel Kitchens to Prove It With Us in 2026.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10">
        The Avorix Cook App is new. What isn't new: our chefs and our processes, which have been running in professional kitchens for years. What we still need are operations whose results we can show. That's why we're making you an offer we'll only extend to the first houses.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/en/contact"
        data-cta-location="hero"
        class="inline-block bg-brand-500 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold text-base hover:bg-brand-600 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-brand-200"
      >
        Request a Pilot Spot
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Offer -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 border-t border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-900 text-center mb-12">The Offer. No Fine Print.</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- You Get -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-neutral-100 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-4">You Get:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>The complete Avorix system — app, recipes, training, ongoing support.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Pilot conditions — roughly half of what we'll charge from 2027.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Direct line to the founder — no ticket system, no call center.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Priority on everything — feature requests, support, customizations.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <!-- We Get -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-neutral-100 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-4">We Get:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Honest feedback — what works, what doesn't, what's missing.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Permission to evaluate and showcase your results anonymously.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 text-center mt-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        If you're also willing to serve as a public reference, we'll discuss a separate deal.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Is It a Fit -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-neutral-50 border-t border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-900 text-center mb-12">Is It a Fit for Your House?</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Fits -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-neutral-100">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-600 mb-4">The pilot program fits if:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>You run a hotel or restaurant in Germany or Austria.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>The skilled labor shortage is a real, tangible problem for you.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>You're willing to change how your kitchen operates — not just install an app.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <!-- Doesn't fit -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-neutral-100">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-4">It's not a fit if:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-600">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-neutral-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
              </svg>
              <span>You run a daily-changing fine-dining menu.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-neutral-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
              </svg>
              <span>You're just looking for an app without changing your processes.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Four Steps -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 border-t border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-900 text-center mb-12">Four Steps to a Kitchen That Always Works.</h2>
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg shrink-0">1</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-1">Introductory Call</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600">30 minutes via video call or phone. We get to know your operation, you get to know our system. Afterward, both sides know whether it's a fit.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg shrink-0">2</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-1">Kitchen Analysis</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600">We review your menu, your processes, and your team. From that, we create a concrete plan for what Avorix can change in your kitchen.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg shrink-0">3</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-1">Onboarding and Training</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600">We digitize your recipes, set up the app, and train your team on-site. No manual, no self-study — we do it together.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg shrink-0">4</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-1">Ongoing Operations</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-600">From here, the system runs. We stay involved, optimize with you, and measure results. You have direct access to us at all times.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Founder -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-neutral-50 border-t border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-900 text-center mb-12">Who's Behind the Offer</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <div class="w-48 h-48 rounded-2xl bg-neutral-200 flex items-center justify-center text-neutral-400">
            <svg class="w-16 h-16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-2">
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Borge Penk, founder of Avorix. Chef, kitchen manager, operations manager — over 15 years in the hospitality industry. Not as a consultant, but as someone who stood at the pass himself and knows what happens when the evening falls apart.
          </p>
          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-brand-500 pl-6 italic text-neutral-600">
            "With the first houses, I'm there in person. Not because I have to, but because I want it to work — and because I learn from every kitchen how to make Avorix better."
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Only 3 -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 border-t border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6">Why Only 3 Spots?</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Because we personally accompany every pilot operation. No scaling at the expense of quality. Three houses where we can be certain the results are right — that's worth more than thirty where we only manage half.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 bg-neutral-50 border-t border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-900 text-center mb-12">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-xl p-4 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
            What does the pilot program cost?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-neutral-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 mt-3 leading-relaxed">Roughly half of what we'll charge from 2027 onward. The exact terms are discussed in the introductory call, as they depend on the size of your operation.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-xl p-4 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
            How long am I committed?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-neutral-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 mt-3 leading-relaxed">The pilot phase runs for 6 months. After that, you decide whether to continue — at the then-current rates. No automatic renewal, no fine print.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-xl p-4 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
            Do I have to serve as a reference?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-neutral-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 mt-3 leading-relaxed">No. We only need permission to evaluate your results anonymously. If you'd also like to appear publicly, we'll make you a separate offer.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-xl p-4 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
            What if it doesn't work for us?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-neutral-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 mt-3 leading-relaxed">Then that's how it is. We're honest: not every kitchen fits our system. If we realize in the introductory call that it's not a match, we'll say so. And if it doesn't work during operations, we'll find a solution together — or end the partnership fairly.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-xl p-4 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between">
            Do I no longer need a head chef?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-neutral-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 mt-3 leading-relaxed">Avorix doesn't replace a head chef. But it ensures your kitchen produces at the right level even when the head chef isn't there — on vacation, on a day off, or when the position is temporarily vacant.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Apply -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 border-t border-neutral-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Request a Pilot Spot. No Obligation.</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 text-lg mb-10">Three minutes. We'll get back to you within two business days.</p>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-neutral-100 shadow-sm p-8 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10 text-left">
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4 font-medium">What we'd like to know from you:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-500 shrink-0"></span>
            Name and position
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-500 shrink-0"></span>
            Business and location
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-500 shrink-0"></span>
            Number of covers per day
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-500 shrink-0"></span>
            Biggest challenge in your kitchen
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-500 shrink-0"></span>
            Preferred contact method
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <a
        href="/en/contact"
        data-cta-location="final"
        class="inline-block bg-brand-500 text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-base hover:bg-brand-600 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-brand-200"
      >
        Request a Pilot Spot
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
